name: Evelynn Default ༺☆༻ (LoRA)
description:
Heyo ૮ ˶´ ᵕˋ ˶づ♡ Really liking doing anime Loras soo here's another league of legends one !!

Requested by @yloo !! Thank you so much for the request !! I really appreciate it ( ˘͈ ᵕ ˘͈♡)

((This Lora does NOT work for photorealistic models))

This Lora works with almost every anime model and semi realistic models !! so go wild with it !! ^^

Please use Trigger words slit_pupils, glowing_eyes, black_sclera, white_hair if your having trouble getting all her features <3

The Lora also works really well with NSFW Prompts !! so have fun with that ! I have a few examples of that as well !! This is not a only NSFW Lora though ૮₍ ˃ ⤙ ˂ ₎ა !!

I recommend keeping the weight at (0.9-0.6) and using the negative prompts as needed !! I've also found it somewhat difficult to get her in different clothing again so I have uploaded a lower epoch version to somewhat help with that (♡ˊ͈ ꒳ ˋ͈).

https://mega.nz/file/Ejp0VKoA#-j3BRCqWjIQl3_d6YQNG0V6tsovfo2_GE08ocP5rh68

Heres a photo example of all the different weights ignore the check marks and such (｡>\\<) !! Click on on me to open a higher res image ! <3

I had so much fun making the Lora and generating the images I hope you have as much fun as I did ⸜(｡˃ ᵕ ˂ )⸝♡ !!!

Please be kind with this Lora ♡

I also highly recommend keeping the weight between (0.9-0.6) and using negative prompts where needed !!

CFG scale: 7

Size: 512x512

Clip skip: 2

Hires upscale: 2

Hires upscaler: R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B

If you have any issues please tell me and ill try and help !! ૮₍ ˶ᵔ ᵕ ᵔ˶ ₎ა
